wPl4o"> <a href="https://en.p2y.jp/hololive-english-1st-concert-connect-the-world-wins-japanese-cabinet-office-cjpf-award-2024/">Hololive英语第一场演唱会-Connect the World-荣获日本内阁府“2024年CJPF奖”</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“hololive English 第一场音乐会 -Connect the World- 荣获日本内阁府“CJPF Award 2024” — P2y.EN" src="https://en.p2y.jp/hololive-english-1st-concert-connect-the-world-wins-japanese-cabinet-office-cjpf-award-2024/embed/#?secret=Pc4yBltwR4#?secret=UYWAwwPl4o" data-secret="UYWAwwPl4o" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p></p>后<a href="https://p2y.jp/hololive-english-1st-concert-connect-the-world-wins-japanese-cabinet-office-cjpf-award-2024/">Hololive 英语第一场音乐会 -Connect the World- 荣获内阁府“CJPF Award 2024”</a>首次出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; https://p2y.jp/hololive-english-1st-concert-connect-the-world-wins-japanese-cabinet-office-cjpf-award-2024/feed/ 0 116887
